==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: memorabilia
<hw>mem`o*ra*bil"i*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>memorabilis</ets> memorable. See <er>Memorable</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Things remarkable and worthy of remembrance or record;
also, the record of them.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Mementos of past events; souvenirs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Memorability</ent>⟦br⟧
